description: Demolition of existing block and erection of part four, part six storey building to provide 412sqm commercial floorspace comprising retail (Use Class A1), financial and professional services (Use Class A2), restaurant / cafe (Use Class A3), business (Use Class B1) and / or non-residential institution (Use Class D1) to the ground floor, together with 78 residential units, car / bicycle parking, refuse / recycling facilities and access, landscaping and amenity proposals.
